\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PARIS\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 414}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Invader\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 472}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 534}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Invader has been cementing his quirky mosaics to Paris walls since the 1990s, usually at night and without permission.\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 655, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 586, \"end\": 591, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999786269, \"rank\": 2.154272113637935e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Invader\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 544}, {\"ngram\": \"his quirky mosaics\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 582}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1990s\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 613}, {\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 631}, {\"ngram\": \"permission\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 654}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's become France's most international, invasive and intriguing contemporary street artist.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 748, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 668, \"end\": 674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9897590988944328, \"rank\": 0.006702281864837991, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His works dot all corners of the City of Light and his fans have a lot of fun hunting them down.\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 845, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His works\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 758}, {\"ngram\": \"all corners\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 774}, {\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 786}, {\"ngram\": \"Light\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 795}, {\"ngram\": \"his fans\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 808}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 819}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And now there is a new, Olympic-themed one for them to find.\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 907, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Invader cemented it to a wall on one of the River Seine's embankments sometime between Tuesday and Wednesday.\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 953, \"end\": 964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Invader\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 916}, {\"ngram\": \"a wall\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 938}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1003}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1017}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Using tiles to create the mosaic, it shows one of his signature Space Invader figures running.\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1083, \"end\": 1096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Space_Invaders\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4996904494181355e-34, \"text\": \"Space Invader\", \"types\": [\"Q7889\", \"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Space_Invaders\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Space_Invaders\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tiles\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1030}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The work's colors evoke the shades of blue that Paris Games organizers have used to decorate the city for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1233, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The work's colors\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1131}, {\"ngram\": \"the shades\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"blue\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1156}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris Games organizers\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1184}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1215}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A representative for artist - who, like him, maintains anonymity - said by email to the Associated Press that \\\"Invader told me to say that he wanted to celebrate the Olympics in Paris with this mosaic.\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1436, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1323, \"end\": 1339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999850947066437, \"rank\": 1.4905515410029943e-05, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 1413, \"end\": 1418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999786269, \"rank\": 2.154272113637935e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A representative\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1251}, {\"ngram\": \"artist\", \"from\": 1256, \"to\": 1262}, {\"ngram\": \"anonymity\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1299}, {\"ngram\": \"email\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1315}, {\"ngram\": \"Invader\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1353}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The space invader is running and he wears some of the colors of the Olympics signage.\\\"\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1523, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The space invader\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1454}, {\"ngram\": \"the colors\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1497}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics signage\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The artist's admirers can download his app, called \\\"Flash Invaders,\\\" and then use it to take photos of any of his works that they find.\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1660, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The artist's admirers\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1546}, {\"ngram\": \"his app\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1567}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Flash Invaders\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1591}, {\"ngram\": \"photos\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1624}, {\"ngram\": \"his works\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1644}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When they do, the app awards them points.\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1703, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The more works they find and \\\"flash,\\\" the more points they get.\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The more works\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1718}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\" the more points\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1757}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's addictive: The app has nearly 400,000 players.\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1820, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The app\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1792}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly 400,000 players\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1819}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The new mosaic is the 1,512th that Invader has glued up in Paris.\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1887, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1881, \"end\": 1886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999786269, \"rank\": 2.154272113637935e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The new mosaic\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1836}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1,512th\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1851}, {\"ngram\": \"Invader\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1864}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Players get 50 points when they flash it with his app.\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1942, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Players\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1895}, {\"ngram\": \"50 points\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1909}, {\"ngram\": \"his app\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since the first catalogued mosaic of a blue Space Invader went up on a Paris street in 1998, numbered PA_01, Invader has colonized the world.\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 2084, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1987, \"end\": 2000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Space_Invaders\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4996904494181355e-34, \"text\": \"Space Invader\", \"types\": [\"Q7889\", \"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Space_Invaders\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Space_Invaders\"}, {\"begin\": 2014, \"end\": 2019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999786269, \"rank\": 2.154272113637935e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PA_01\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2050}, {\"ngram\": \"Invader\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2059}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are now more than 4,000 of his mosaics in cities and towns on all continents except Antarctica.\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2186, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his mosaics\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2129}, {\"ngram\": \"cities\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2139}, {\"ngram\": \"towns\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2149}, {\"ngram\": \"all continents\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2167}, {\"ngram\": \"Antarctica\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2185}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Instagram, the artist posted a photo Wednesday of the new work and the words \\\"Special Olympic Games Paris 2024,\\\" with a jogger running past.That and a video post by the artist alerted admirers that there was a new work for them to find.\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2427, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2191, \"end\": 2200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.831213321336807e-25, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the artist\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2212}, {\"ngram\": \"a photo\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2227}, {\"ngram\": \"the new work\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2253}, {\"ngram\": \"the words\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2267}, {\"ngram\": \"Special Olympic Games Paris\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2296}, {\"ngram\": \"a jogger\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2317}, {\"ngram\": \"a video post\", \"from\": 2340, \"to\": 2352}, {\"ngram\": \"the artist\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2366}, {\"ngram\": \"admirers\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2383}, {\"ngram\": \"a new work\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A small group of them quickly tracked it down, took its photo with the app, got their points, and spent time together admiring the work.\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2565, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A small group\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2442}, {\"ngram\": \"its photo\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2490}, {\"ngram\": \"the app\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2503}, {\"ngram\": \"their points\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2521}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2537}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2564}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Super fan Andr\\u00e9 Lavigne, a 64-year-old retired chemical engineer, was among the first to find and flash it.\", \"from\": 2567, \"to\": 2674, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Super fan Andr\\u00e9 Lavigne\", \"from\": 2567, \"to\": 2590}, {\"ngram\": \"a 64-year-old retired chemical engineer\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2631}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is currently ranked in the top 100 players on the app, having tracked down 2,718 of the artist's works in France and overseas.\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2804, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2784, \"end\": 2790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9897590988944328, \"rank\": 0.006702281864837991, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the top 100 players\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2720}, {\"ngram\": \"the app\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2731}, {\"ngram\": \"the artist's works\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In just the first few hours, the work was already generated buzz.\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2871, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just the first few hours\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2833}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 2835, \"to\": 2843}, {\"ngram\": \"buzz\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2870}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have seen many people coming and flashing and asking, 'It's a new one?'\", \"from\": 2873, \"to\": 2947, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many people\", \"from\": 2886, \"to\": 2897}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I say, 'Yes, it has been put (up) last night.'\", \"from\": 2948, \"to\": 2998, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(They reply) 'Oh, well, that's extraordinary,\\\" Lavigne said.\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3059, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lavigne\", \"from\": 3046, \"to\": 3053}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another admirer, Gema Calero, rolled up on her bike and celebrated with a fist pump when she got her 50 points.\", \"from\": 3061, \"to\": 3172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3083, \"end\": 3089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kiko_Calero\", \"score\": 0.992801745079605, \"rank\": 0.00725044546692116, \"text\": \"Calero\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kiko_Calero\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kiko_Calero\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another admirer\", \"from\": 3061, \"to\": 3076}, {\"ngram\": \"her bike\", \"from\": 3104, \"to\": 3112}, {\"ngram\": \"a fist pump\", \"from\": 3133, \"to\": 3144}, {\"ngram\": \"her 50 points\", \"from\": 3158, \"to\": 3171}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's all fresh, it still smells of glue,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3174, \"to\": 3226, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"glue\", \"from\": 3210, \"to\": 3214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She says searching high and low across Paris for the works has taught her lots about the city and the value of looking around.\", \"from\": 3228, \"to\": 3354, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3267, \"end\": 3272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999786269, \"rank\": 2.154272113637935e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the works\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3286}, {\"ngram\": \"her lots\", \"from\": 3298, \"to\": 3306}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 3313, \"to\": 3321}, {\"ngram\": \"the value\", \"from\": 3326, \"to\": 3335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It allows you to look at life differently.\", \"from\": 3356, \"to\": 3399, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 3382, \"to\": 3386}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You hunt around.\", \"from\": 3400, \"to\": 3416, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You look up a little bit.\", \"from\": 3417, \"to\": 3442, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Because normally when we walk we look at what's in front of us,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3443, \"to\": 3517, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 3494, \"to\": 3499}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3503, \"to\": 3505}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's super.\\\"\", \"from\": 3518, \"to\": 3531, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Like Banksy, the British street artist he is sometimes likened to, Invader is elusive, fiercely protective of his anonymity and operating on the margins of illegality.\", \"from\": 3533, \"to\": 3700, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3538, \"end\": 3544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Banksy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Banksy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Banksy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Banksy\"}, {\"begin\": 3550, \"end\": 3557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999524481696739, \"rank\": 4.711683427927441e-05, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Invader\", \"from\": 3600, \"to\": 3607}, {\"ngram\": \"his anonymity\", \"from\": 3643, \"to\": 3656}, {\"ngram\": \"the margins\", \"from\": 3674, \"to\": 3685}, {\"ngram\": \"illegality\", \"from\": 3689, \"to\": 3699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He comes, glues, and disappears into the night, leaving behind his signature pixelated mosaics made mostly with small ceramic and glass tiles.\", \"from\": 3701, \"to\": 3843, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"glues\", \"from\": 3711, \"to\": 3716}, {\"ngram\": \"the night\", \"from\": 3738, \"to\": 3747}, {\"ngram\": \"his signature pixelated mosaics\", \"from\": 3764, \"to\": 3795}, {\"ngram\": \"small ceramic and glass tiles\", \"from\": 3813, \"to\": 3842}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most resemble the aliens from the Space Invaders arcade game.\", \"from\": 3845, \"to\": 3906, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3879, \"end\": 3893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Space_Invaders\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1852458597223756e-35, \"text\": \"Space Invaders\", \"types\": [\"Q7889\", \"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Space_Invaders\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Space_Invaders\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the aliens\", \"from\": 3859, \"to\": 3869}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Others are wonderfully elaborate, such as still lives of fruit or, in New York, portraits of Lou Reed and Andy Warhol.\", \"from\": 3907, \"to\": 4025, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3977, \"end\": 3985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999997461409615, \"rank\": 2.538584188143923e-07, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 4000, \"end\": 4008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lou_Reed\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3332481530531815e-35, \"text\": \"Lou Reed\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lou_Reed\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lou_Reed\"}, {\"begin\": 4013, \"end\": 4024, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Warhol\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0774540287371338e-38, \"text\": \"Andy Warhol\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Warhol\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Warhol\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Others\", \"from\": 3907, \"to\": 3913}, {\"ngram\": \"still lives\", \"from\": 3949, \"to\": 3960}, {\"ngram\": \"fruit\", \"from\": 3964, \"to\": 3969}, {\"ngram\": \"portraits\", \"from\": 3987, \"to\": 3996}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some reference pop culture - Spider-Man, Star Wars, Bugs Bunny, Ninja Turtles, pizza and the like.\", \"from\": 4026, \"to\": 4124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4078, \"end\": 4088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bugs_Bunny\", \"score\": 0.9999999036635974, \"rank\": 9.633621781791108e-08, \"text\": \"Bugs Bunny\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bugs_Bunny\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bugs_Bunny\"}, {\"